HEADWORD: Hucksterage
<hw>Huck"ster*age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The business of
a huckster; small dealing; peddling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Ignoble <qex>huckster</qex> age of piddling tithes.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hucksterer</ent>⟦br⟧
